snippet.title: 14 Locks (Walkthrough) - Bontegames
snippet.description:
I am not the maker, I am just recording a walkthrough
To save you some time, after 5:50 it is just credits.
Made by using the Unity 3d player

You can play the game here: http://bartbonte.com/14locks/
More games by Bonte: www.bontegames.com
More info on bontegames is in the video on his credits.

Recorded with hypercam. Sound starts to go off synch after 5minutes so please ignore that.
